banco btg pactual sa private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of banco btg pactual sa snapshot people company overview banco btg pactual sa together with its subsidiaries provides financial products and services in brazil and internationally the company’s investment banking services include underwriting of public and private debt and equity products advisory services relating to mergers and acquisitions divestitures restructurings spinoffs reorganizations and other corporate transactions placement and advisory services in public and private offers of equity and debt bonds credit products and instruments including export credit lines collateralized loans repos bridge loans securitization guarantees and others as well as alternative fixed income investments financial products and service banco btg pactual sa together with its subsidiaries provides financial products and services in brazil and internationally the company’s investment banking services include underwriting of public and private debt and equity products advisory services relating to mergers and acquisitions divestitures restructurings spinoffs reorganizations and other corporate transactions placement and advisory services in public and private offers of equity and debt bonds credit products and instruments including export credit lines collateralized loans repos bridge loans securitization guarantees and others as well as alternative fixed income investments financial products and services in stocks fixed income and equities interest rates and foreign exchange and commodities and market making brokerage and research services its asset management products and services comprise equity hedge and fixed income investment funds management of investment funds private equity infrastructure real estate and natural resource investment funds and administration of investment funds the company’s wealth management services include banking and transaction products such as credit lines bank guarantees government bonds bank deposit certificates corporate bonds real estate credit bills and notes agricultural credit bills and stocks and stock loans as well as exchange traded and overthecounter derivatives structured notes and foreign exchange spot and futures market services portfolio investment solutions and wealth and estate planning and retirement services as well as advisory services for tax efficiency succession planning offshore investment solutions and philanthropic projects it also offers corporate advisory services in the areas of funding and strategic consulting the company was founded in  and is based in sao paulo brazil banco btg pactual sa is a subsidiary of btg pactual holding sa detailed description av brigadeiro faria lima º andar  itaim bibisao paulo sp brazilfounded in  phone     wwwbtgpactualcom key executives for banco btg pactual sa mr roberto balls sallouti ceo member of board of executive officers  director age  mr marcelo kalim chairman of the board senior vp  member of board of executive officers mr joão marcello dantas leite executive officer cfo iro  member of board of executive officers mr antonio carlos canto porto filho senior vp executive officer  member of board of executive officers mr guilherme da costa paes cohead of the investment banking unit executive officer  member of board of executive officers compensation as of fiscal year  banco btg pactual sa key developments btg pactual presents at investing in latam mining cumbre jul  pm jun   btg pactual presents at investing in latam mining cumbre jul  pm venue santiago chile speakers nicolas de camino director ­ asset management banco btg pactual sa announces unaudited earnings results for the first quarter of  may   banco btg pactual sa announced unaudited earnings results for the first quarter of  total revenue was brl  million against brl  million a quarter ago adjusted net income was brl  million against brl  million a quarter ago adjusted income before