nt and board of directors overview banco btg pactual btg pactual participations committees overview btg pactual is structured as two separate subgroups of commonly owned entities i banco btg pactual and ii btg pactual participations which is the general partner of and controls btgi however the two subgroups are managed in a strategically unified manner for the benefit of the overall enterprise top banco btg pactual board of directors the board of directors of banco btg pactual is responsible for among other things electing and removing the executive officers and supervising the other members of banco btg pactual’s management team the table below shows the name and position of each member elected to the board of directors of banco btg pactual as well as a summary of members‘ businesses experience and other biographical information name position election date marcelo kalim chairman of the board april   marcelo kalim is the chairman of the board of directors of banco btg pactual and btg pactual participations in addition mr kalim is senior vice president of banco btg pactual and btg pactual participations mr kalim joined banco btg pactual in  and became a partner in  mr kalim served as chief investment officer of banco btg pactual from  to  where he was responsible for investment decisions in the funds managed by banco btg pactual mr kalim began his career at banco btg pactual as a fixedincome trader and served as head fund manager and cohead of btg pactual asset management mr kalim received his bachelor’s degree in economics from the university of s�o paulo and his mba from the massachusetts institute of technology sloan school of management roberto balls sallouti director april   roberto sallouti is the chief executive officer and a member of the board of directors of btg pactual mr sallouti joined the firm in  and became a partner in  he was named chief operating officer in  having previously been responsible for the firm’s fixed income division he was named chief e